				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. oe debugbook\r\nset quest flags & option\r\nact 1\r\nGOB- Goblin Camp\r\nTortured Adventurer\r\n4. Persuade the torturer and teleport me to the adventurer\r\n5. Talk to adventurer"
				},
